string-array.name: dubbisa1
string-array.item: SEENSA SEERA YAKKAA Seerri adabbii bara 1957 hojiirra erga oolee gara walakkaa jaarraa tokkootti dhiyaateera. Yeroo kana keessatti jijjiiramni hundee siyaasaa, diinagdee fi hawaasummaa Itoophiyaa keessatti mul’ateera. Jijjiiramoota gurguddoo keessaa Heera mootummaa fi waliigalteewwan idil-addunyaa Itoophiyaan raggaasifteen walqixxummaa amantiiwwan saboota, sablammootaa fi ummatoota, mirga dimokiraasii fi bilisummaa lammiilee fi jiraattotaa, mirga namoomaa, hunda caalaa immoo mirga gareewwan hawaasaa beekamtii kennuudha akka dubartootaa fi daa’immanii. Taateewwan kun hundi erga raawwatamanii booda raawwiin seera adabbii bara 1949 bahe itti fufuu hayyamuun sirrii hin ta’u. Qaawwi seera adabbii keessatti mul’atu kan biraan yakkoota guddina teeknooloojii fi walxaxiinsa jireenya ammayyaa irraa dhalatan sirnaan furuu dhabuu isaati. Seerri adabbii yakkoota akka xiyyaara butachuu, yakka kompiitaraa fi maallaqa seeraan alaa daddabarsuu hin hammatu. Kana malees, yakkoota malaammaltummaa fi qoricha sammuu namaa hadoochu waliin walqabatan ilaalchisee yeroo ammaa kana ta’us, daangaa biyyaa keessatti qofa osoo hin taane sadarkaa naannoo fi idil-addunyaattis seera baasuu fi hordoffii keessatti xiyyeeffannoo hawwataa kan jiran yoo ta’u, rakkoo hamaa isaan geessisaa jiran irraa kan ka’e, seera adabbii yakkoota akkasii sadarkaa cimina isaaniif malutiin haala gahaa ta’een hin ilaalu. Qabxiin biraa bira darbamuu hin qabne seera adabbii sababa gocha aadaa miidhaa geessiseen miidhaa fi gidiraa cimaa dubartootaa fi daa’imman irra ga’eef beekamtii kennuu dhabuu isaati. Dhugaadha, Heerri mootummaa aadaa ummatootaaf kabaja akka qabaatu kan mirkaneessu ta’us, gochoota miidhaa akka qaban saayinsiidhaan mirkanaa’an sana hin deggeru. Seera imaanaa fi deeggarsa ummataa hin qabne baasuunis bu’aa hin qabu sababiin isaas yeroo baay’ee hojiirra ooluu kan hin dandeenye ta’ee hafeera. Garuu qaamni seera baasu yeroo tokko tokko seera tarkaanfataa fudhachuudhaan ummanni gochaalee aadaa miidhaa geessisan irraa akka adda ba’uuf barsiisuu fi qajeelchuu akka qabu falaasama seera yakkaa keessatti beekamtii guddaa qaba.

Histogram equalisation  Equalization increases the global contrast of many images, especially when the usable data of the image is represented by close contrast values.  Through this adjustment, the intensities can be better distributed on the histogram.This allows for areas of lower local contrast to gain a higher contrast.  Histogram equalization accomplishes this by effectively spreading out the most frequent intensity values. The method is useful in images with backgrounds and foregrounds that are both bright or both dark. In particular, the method can lead to better views of bone structure in x- ray images
